snippet.title: Minecraft Super Mario Mash-Up Pack for Wii U
snippet.description: On May 17, the Super Mario Mash-Up Pack comes to Minecraft: Wii U Edition as a free game update. Download the update to get new skins, a Super Mario-themed pre-made world and a set of Super Mario-themed music and item textures!
